              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Neither the conversion rate lift (+0.9pp, p = 0.82) nor the AOV difference (−£0.49, p = 0.96) reached statistical significance at alpha = 0.05. The confidence intervals overlap heavily and the experiment is massively underpowered: 463 total orders against the required 14,988. At this dataset’s traffic volume (~12 orders per day), detecting a 5% AOV lift would require over 1,200 days on live traffic. No guardrail breaches were observed: treatment return rate did not exceed control by more than 3 percentage points.",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontFamily": "Segoe UI",
                      "fontSize": "10pt"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
